name: Marsixer Mielsch
description: The sweetest character a girl can have! I can say I’m very passionate, emotional and sensitive. I can explode fast but at the same time I move on easily. I like to make people smile and happy, I’m a good listener and support. I like to laugh. I’m pretty active. But if I’m tired sometimes I enjoy a quiet evening. In general I like to have a positive view on the world.
